<span style="font-style: italic;">Free event, open to the public</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Brookline, MA</span><br />
April 5, 7:00 pm<br />
Talk + Booksigning<br />
<a href="http://www.brooklinebooksmith-shop.com/about-us">Brookline Booksmith</a><br />
