<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">New York, NY</span><br />
April 6, 7:00 pm<br />
Talk + Booksigning<br />
<a href="http://www.posmanbooks.com/site/store-locations-hours/">Posman Books at Chelsea Market</a><br />
<span style="font-style: italic;">Free event, open to the public</span></p>
