    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, i started reading your book yesterday and finished it this morning-LOVED IT!! The paperback version was a great idea-your writing is awesome and the recipes, well I don&#39;t know where to start-actually I do know where-with your last recipe &#8211; your wedding cake&#8230;thanks for sharing your life, your love of food and the love of your life with all of us!</p>
    </div>

